item.title: Sydney Sweeney Recruits Her German Shepherd Puppy for Cameo in New American Eagle Campaign
item.description: The actress and in-demand brand partner helped design the “Sydney Jean,” with 100 percent of net proceeds donated to Crisis Text Line, a free mental health support and crisis intervention phone line.
